{"id": "1469026743263432861", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 19, "author_id": "332573289438380032", "author_name": "moyashi0672", "author_bot": false, "content": "- Check relic\n- Check units\n- Check WoD\n- See if there is some combo between units + WoD or units + units\n- Sometimes the combo can get bricked by the relic\n- Posse are situational, but some are extremely good to have stuff like stagnation 3 pierce or void\n- Aim for counterpick, If the enemy take strike based unit then you take para posse stuff like that\n- Based on the relic you change your playstyle, for example you got the relic that reshuffle your hand every turns, you discards all of your high cost wheel if you have more than 2 or 3 in starting hand", "timestamp": "2026-02-05T17:47:48.791000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-02-05T17:50:00.338000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["266065777633787905"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1468971059809095700", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
